Welcome to Panorama Village

The City of Panorama Village was originally designed as a premier golfing community in the early 1960s and quickly became a weekend haven from the hustle and bustle of a large metropolitan city. In 1972, Panorama Village was incorporated as a Type A general city, quickly developing into the cherished community that it is today.

Panorama Village was established in the early 1960’s and became a incorporated city in 1972. This is a general law city with a City Council consisting of a Mayor and 5 councilpersons as the governing body. We have our own Police Department and a Utility Department which operates our independent water and sewer system. The city is a taxing authority and the utility department and golf club operate as “Enterprise Funds” generally funding the necessary operations for these functions.
